title: Ministry of Sound House Party 2014 (2013) (320kbps) (AciDToX8)
description:
Ministry of Sound: House Party 2014 (2013) 

                      House, Dance | Ministry Of Sound

             320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013 | 14:03:20 | 1.16 Gb


Cripes! Ministry have wrapped up a one hundred song festive mix to cater for all your seasonal parties and even NYE too! The comp is broken down to a series of mixes in different styles with one featuring the big recent pop hits from Avicii and Example. There's also a Club Classics mix with Fat Boy Slim and Eric Prydz, a Trance one with heavy hitters from Sander Van Doorn and Tiesto, a Bass Heavy mix with DJ Fresh, Andy C and Shy FX and finally there's even an Underground Sounds mix with tracks from X-Press 2 and Alex Kenji.
